name: MyWEBoo
overview:
MyWEBoo seeks to provide an easier and more convenient way to manage data across all different social portals and control personal world is shown to the rest of the world.

We recognize that the everyday person has files and data located on Facebook, Flickr, Google Docs, PCs, and many other places. The userâ€™s files and data are extremely cluttered while their friends have difficulties finding and following user across multiple sites. MyWEBoo, our solution, is a Personal Management Center where users can plug in web services as Drives and manage their contents stored on Facebook, Youtube, and other platforms all in one place. We then aggregate their pictures, videos, streams, social networks, and data we collect to push out monster profiles / feeds for each user. We aim to help people better manage both of their personal and public worlds.
